Welcome to the Law Office of Thomas H. Edwards
California Employment Rights Lawyer

Employment Law Attorney Serving Southern California
If you have questions about your rights as an employee or any other matter, you deserve answers from a veteran trial lawyer with more than 30 years of experience.
I am a California attorney representing clients in Los Angeles and throughout Southern California. My employment law practice is focused on cases involving employee rights, including the right to be paid overtime, the right to meal periods and rest periods, and the right to work without being subjected to unlawful discrimination, harassment or retaliation. I also handle cases in other practice areas, including business and contract disputes, fraud claims, real estate and construction disputes, copyright infringement and personal injury and wrongful death lawsuits.
I am a sole practitioner, and I am personally responsible for all of the work performed on every case I handle. I know how important your case is to you, and I promise that your case will be just as important to me as it is to you.
Get More Information About Your Rights
I offer a free and confidential initial consultation to all potential clients. To make an appointment or to talk to me about your case, call me toll free at 866.277.9861. You may also contact me online.





Thomas H. Edwards119 E. Union StreetSuite BPasadena, CA 91103T: (626) 395-5161T: (866) 277-9861
  


