VOTED “ALABAMA SUPER LAWYER” AGAIN FOR 2011, 2012 and NOW 2013!


Attorney, Advocate, Adviser

Tom Edwards is an Alabama Attorney at Law – Fighting for “Justice” in America. With a proven record of *Professionalism and Successful Litigation.” Tom gains maximum recovery for his clients’ claims, both quickly and fairly, often without going to court.  

 



Accident and Injury Law
 


You may need a Qualified Alabama Injury Attorney if:

You sustained an injury in an automobile accident.
You are in a workers’ comp case.
You were injured on-the-job.
You were harmed by a defective product or a drug.
You slipped and fell at a store.
You have lost a loved in an industrial or motor vehicle accident.
You were mistreated by an insurance company.


Tom Edwards has a proven record of success.
A record that works for clients often in fast and significant settlements without going to court!
Call Us at: 334-215-1011
